    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required Gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly permitted to remain at Gradation 1 under ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 for MRL 2 Class II devices. GCI of 2.7 % and mean NIH error of 8.3 % are within pre-defined acceptance bands. The simulation evidence is judged sufficient to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application.",
